{
  "id": "6a0fc9a04deb7fdf09562a69",
  "title": "コドン表とアミノ酸を視覚的に見る",
  "created": 1779419558,
  "updated": 1779427570,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a0fc9a04deb7fdf09562a69",
      "text": "コドン表とアミノ酸を視覚的に見る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779419558,
      "updated": 1779419558
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fe8f00000000000a36f41",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779427570,
      "updated": 1779427570
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fc9a60000000000ee80ed",
      "text": "アミノ酸の化学式や分子モデルをコドン表といっしょに並べると、なにか面白いものが見えてくるかもしれない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779419560,
      "updated": 1779419650
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fc9ab0000000000ee80ee",
      "text": "仮説：コドン表セントラルドグマの何処かの過程でミスが生じた時に影響が少ないロバストな配置になっているのではないか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779419565,
      "updated": 1779419802
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fca020000000000ee80ef",
      "text": "\t記号的にみると特定の位置の塩基がドントケアになっているものがある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779419652,
      "updated": 1779419879
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd3b600000000009cdaff",
      "text": "\t\ttable:コドン逆対照表",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779422136,
      "updated": 1779422154
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd3ca00000000009cdb00",
      "text": "   3字\t1字\t呼称\t性質\t縮重\tコドン (具体的な表現)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779422155,
      "updated": 1779423031
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd79d00000000009cdb2b",
      "text": "   Phe\tF\tフェニルアラニン\t非極\tUU[UC[⁣]]\tUUU、UUC",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423134,
      "updated": 1779423293
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd8fa00000000009cdbd3",
      "text": "   Leu\tL\tロイシン1\t非極\tUU[AG[⁣]]\tUUA、UUG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423484,
      "updated": 1779423500
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd7a200000000009cdb38",
      "text": "   Ser\tS\tセリン1\t極性\tUC*\tUCU、UCC、UCA、UCG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423139,
      "updated": 1779423484
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd7a800000000009cdb46",
      "text": "   Tyr\tY\tチロシン\t極性\tUA[UC[⁣]]\tUAU、UAC",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423146,
      "updated": 1779423405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd91200000000009cdbd5",
      "text": "   ---\t-\t終止コドン1\t\tUA[AG[⁣]]\tUAA、UAG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423508,
      "updated": 1779423525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fdaa000000000009cdc0f",
      "text": "   Trp\tW\tトリプトファン\t非極\tUGG\tUGG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423905,
      "updated": 1779423905
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd97f00000000009cdbe3",
      "text": "   ---\t-\t終止コドン2\t\tUGA\tUGA",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423616,
      "updated": 1779423616
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fda0700000000009cdc0a",
      "text": "   Cys\tC\tシステイン\t極性\tUG[UC[⁣]]\tUGU、UGC",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423753,
      "updated": 1779423753
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd9c500000000009cdbea",
      "text": "   Arg\tR\tアルギニン1\t塩基\tCG*\tAGA、AGG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423686,
      "updated": 1779423686
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd9c900000000009cdbf0",
      "text": "   Gln\tQ\tグルタミン\t極性\tCA[AG[⁣]]\tCAA、CAG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423690,
      "updated": 1779423690
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd9cb00000000009cdbf3",
      "text": "   His\tH\tヒスチジン\t塩基\tCA[UC[⁣]]\tCAU、CAC",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423692,
      "updated": 1779423692
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd9cd00000000009cdbf7",
      "text": "   Pro\tP\tプロリン\t非極\tCC*\tCCU、CCC、CCA、CCG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423694,
      "updated": 1779423694
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd9ce00000000009cdbf8",
      "text": "   Leu\tL\tロイシン2\t非極\tCU*\tCUU、CUC、CUA、CUG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423696,
      "updated": 1779423696
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd9bc00000000009cdbe4",
      "text": "   Ile\tI\tイソロイシン\t非極\tAU[UCA[⁣]]\tAUU、AUC、AUA",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423678,
      "updated": 1779423698
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd7f900000000009cdb9d",
      "text": "   Met\tM\tメチオニン\t非極\tAUG\tAUG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423227,
      "updated": 1779423309
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd81b00000000009cdbb9",
      "text": "   ---\t-\t開始コドン\t\tAUG\tAUG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423260,
      "updated": 1779423260
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd7fd00000000009cdba4",
      "text": "   Thr\tT\tトレオニン\t極性\tAC*\tACU、ACC、ACA、ACG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423231,
      "updated": 1779423355
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd7ff00000000009cdba5",
      "text": "   Asn\tN\tアスパラギン\t極性\tAA[UC[⁣]]\tAAU、AAC",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423233,
      "updated": 1779423233
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd80400000000009cdbaa",
      "text": "   Lys\tK\tリシン\t塩基\tAA[AG[⁣]]\tAAA、AAG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423237,
      "updated": 1779423365
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd8e600000000009cdbd2",
      "text": "   Arg\tR\tアルギニン2\t塩基\tAG[AG[⁣]]\tCGU、CGC、CGA、CGG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423463,
      "updated": 1779423463
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fda2800000000009cdc0c",
      "text": "   Ser\tS\tセリン2\t極性\tAG[UC[⁣]]\tAGU、AGC",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423786,
      "updated": 1779423786
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd9de00000000009cdbfe",
      "text": "   Gly\tG\tグリシン\t親水\tGG*\tGGU、GGC、GGA、GGG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423711,
      "updated": 1779423711
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd9e100000000009cdc02",
      "text": "   Glu\tE\tグルタミン酸\t酸性\tGA[AG[⁣]]\tGAA、GAG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423714,
      "updated": 1779423714
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd9e300000000009cdc05",
      "text": "   Asp\tD\tアスパラギン酸\t酸性\tGA[UC[⁣]]\tGAU、GAC",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423716,
      "updated": 1779423716
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd9e600000000009cdc08",
      "text": "   Val\tV\tバリン\t非極\tGU*\tGUU、GUC、GUA、GUG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423719,
      "updated": 1779423719
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fda3200000000009cdc0d",
      "text": "   Ala\tA\tアラニン\t非極\tGC*\tGCU、GCC、GCA、GCG",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423795,
      "updated": 1779423795
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd9d800000000009cdbf9",
      "text": "\t分子の形状を並べることで更に似た形状のアミノ酸のコドンが似た配列になっていることが確認できるのではないか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779423705,
      "updated": 1779423721
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fced300000000009cdaef",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779420884,
      "updated": 1779420884
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fe81e00000000009cdc2c",
      "text": "Wikipedia に惜しいのがある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779427359,
      "updated": 1779427359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fe81e00000000009cdc2d",
      "text": "\t> [https://gyazo.com/55426a81174ae470cc8b3b31f6caa1f1]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779427359,
      "updated": 1779427359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fe81e00000000009cdc2e",
      "text": " > [https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/コドン コドン]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779427359,
      "updated": 1779427359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fe81e00000000009cdc2f",
      "text": "\t順番をグレイコードにするともっと連続性が上がるのに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779427359,
      "updated": 1779427359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fe81e00000000009cdc30",
      "text": "\t\t例えば最初の文字が U, A である領域を逆順にすると時計回りに ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779427359,
      "updated": 1779427359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fe81e00000000009cdc31",
      "text": "\t\t\tStop, [$ \\color{#0c0}\\rm C], Stops, [$ \\color{#0c0}\\rm Y], [$ \\color{#0c0}\\rm S] [$ \\color{#f80}\\rm L], [$ \\color{#f80}\\rm F], [$ \\color{#f80}\\rm W], [$ \\color{#f80}\\rm L], [$ \\color{#f80}\\rm P,] [$ \\color{#88f}\\rm H], [$ \\color{#0c0}\\rm Q], [$ \\color{#88f}\\rm R] [$ \\color{#88f}\\rm R], [$ \\color{#0c0}\\rm S], [$ \\color{#88f}\\rm K], [$ \\color{#0c0}\\rm N], [$ \\color{#0c0}\\rm T], [$ \\color{#f80}\\rm M], [$ \\color{#f80}\\rm I], [$ \\color{#f80}\\rm V], [$ \\color{#f80}\\rm A], [$ \\color{#f88}\\rm D], [$ \\color{#f88}\\rm E], [$ \\color{#0c0}\\rm G]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779427359,
      "updated": 1779427359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fe81e00000000009cdc32",
      "text": "\t\t\tオレンジの領域の分断がなくなる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779427359,
      "updated": 1779427359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fe82200000000009cdc33",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779427364,
      "updated": 1779427364
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fe82200000000009cdc34",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779427364,
      "updated": 1779427364
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fcb280000000000ee80f2",
      "text": "横に並べたいのでここで作業するには向かないかもしれない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779419946,
      "updated": 1779427364
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fcb4e0000000000ee80f4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779419984,
      "updated": 1779420023
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fced500000000009cdaf0",
      "text": "並べる順番を考えないと",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779420886,
      "updated": 1779421862
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd2a600000000009cdafe",
      "text": "\t既存のよくある表の並びに不満がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779421864,
      "updated": 1779421872
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd29c00000000009cdafc",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/a9ed1892837e28ba707442c9af72720b]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779421853,
      "updated": 1779427369
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fe82700000000009cdc35",
      "text": "\t\t親水性、疎水性、酸、塩基と芳香族環の有無を取り敢えず表示してみた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779427369,
      "updated": 1779427468
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd29c00000000009cdafd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779421853,
      "updated": 1779421853
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fcef700000000009cdaf6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779420920,
      "updated": 1779421844
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd29200000000009cdafa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779421844,
      "updated": 1779421844
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0fd29300000000009cdafb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779421844,
      "updated": 1779421844
    }
  ]
}